text: Muchetbar () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Dmitriyevsky Selsoviet, Zilairsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 70 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 42 km from Zilair, 10 km from Dmitriyevka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zilairsky District
title: Muchetbar
